snippet.title: Best Play Pro Yakyuu II (Famicom) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full exhibition game of Best Play Pro Yakyuu II, a 1990 baseball management game for the Family Computer by ASCII. Rare to see an 8-bit console game with no human control over the players, but this is a pure management game like Out of the Park Baseball. I'm letting the computer make the management decisions for both teams in this video.
